data.description: Experience the expansive .68-acre lot either from the inviting covered front porch or transform the additional space into a flourishing garden. Engage in creative pursuits, construction projects, or recreational activities within the dedicated 30x48 pole barn situated on its own parcel, providing ample room for diverse endeavors. The residence comprises two bedrooms, one bath, an unfinished basement, and a convenient step-saver kitchen. Further enhancing the allure of the property is an extra detached garage, contributing to its overall appeal.
